        </a>
        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/anandubabukr"
          class="flex items-center mr-3"
        >
          <img
            src="/assets/icons/resume-ln.svg"
            class="w-3 h-3 mr-2"
            alt="LinkedIn"
          />
          in/anandubabukr
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/anandubabu-kr/"
          class="flex items-center mr-3"
        >
          <img
            src="/assets/icons/resume-gh.svg"
            class="w-3 h-3 mr-2"
            alt="LinkedIn"
          />

          gh/anandubabu-kr
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
    <!-- summery -->
    <p contenteditable="true" class="pt-2">
      Frontend-focused Fullstack Engineer, boasting over three years of
      proficiency in Next.js, React.js, and Astro.js. Adept in crafting
      intricate applications, guiding agile teams, and ensuring application
      security. Designed user interfaces, constructed gateway APIs, and expertly
      managed version control with Git/GitLab, consistently delivering
      high-performance web solutions.
    </p>
    <!-- exp -->
    <section class="w-full">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-center border-b border-slate-200 pb-2">
        Experience
      </h3>

      <!-- ECS -->
      <article class="mt-3">
        <div class="flex justify-between">
          <h1 class="font-bold text-normal">
            <span class="text-blue-700"> Frontend Engineer</span> @ ECS Business
            Solutions.
          </h1>
          <h2 class="text-xs uppercase">AuGUST 2022 – PRESENT</h2>
        </div>
        <ul contenteditable="true" class="ml-6 list-disc list-outside">
          <li>
            Crafted a scalable frontend architecture for React.js and Next.js
            applications, prioritizing maintainability, reusability, and
            readability.
          </li>
          <li>
            Developed Express.js gateway APIs to connect with Spring
            microservices, improving data access and security. Supported backend
            team in achieving REST API standards.
          </li>
          <li>
            Utilizing the antd component library for apps with theming and
            branding for banking and finance-related applications.
          </li>
          <li>
            Designed application products and user interfaces using Figma,
            delivering intuitive and customer-centric interfaces for complex
            interactions that met and exceeded expectations.
