                Utilized cutting-edge tech stack to maintain and enhance the
                application, ensuring regular updates for packages and bug
                fixes.
              </li>
              <li>
                Implemented Electron-Vite to optimize the desktop application,
                leveraged Tailwind CSS for UI design, and conducted API testing
                using Postman.
              </li>
              <li>
                Implemented security measures across various features including
                laundry management, employee management, customer management,
                etc.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>

